F&P Healthcare May Face Industrial Action From 900 Workers

-- B y   T r a c y   W i t h e r s
-- 
2011-09-16T04:36:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/f-p-healthcare-may-face-industrial-action-from-900-workers.html
Fisher & Paykel Healthcare Corp.
may face industrial action from as many as 900 workers at a
plant in Auckland, according to their unions.  Production, maintenance and distribution workers have
lodged a strike notice to take effect Sept. 21 after failing to
reach agreement at talks yesterday, the Engineering, Printing
and Manufacturing Union said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tracy Withers at 
 twithers@bloomberg.net  